Yamalo-Nenets, Russia Climate

Weather: 14.65°C/58.37°F, Wind SW at 2.89 km/h, 74% Humidity, 0.17% Chance of rain

Yamalo-Nenets Climate Summary

Located at an elevation of 29.01 meters (95.18 feet) above sea level, Yamalo-Nenets has a Subartic, severe winter, no dry season, cool summer climate (Classification: Dfc). The city’s yearly temperature is -3.41ºC (25.86ºF) and it is -8.68% lower than Russia’s averages. Yamalo-Nenets typically receives about 61.69 millimeters (2.43 inches) of precipitation and has 147.37 rainy days (40.38% of the time) annually.
